name: Portraits-Avatar: Metahuman Freaking Out
description: UHD 4K gif (2160x3840) for vertical displays, by Tono C @toocabanelas. Portraits-Avatar is a series of virtual experiments that reflects on our second (or first) digital identity: avatars, metahumans, transhumans. It is based on portraits that combine ancient photographic or cinematographic techniques with video game programming, 3D scanning, AI and Deep Learning.
